#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`quarkus.oidc.certificate-chain.leaf-certificate-name` can also require that the trustore contains a leaf chain certificate."
